headline: Dell Technologies (DELL): A Fresh Look at Valuation Following CFO Transition and Continued AI Growth Momentum
summary: For anyone holding shares of Dell Technologies (DELL) or thinking about jumping in, a major leadership transition is in the spotlight this week. Dell announced that Chief Financial Officer Yvonne McGill will step down, with longtime executive David Kennedy stepping in as interim CFO while the company searches for a permanent replacement. Importantly, the company made it clear there were no disagreements about financial matters behind the move and quickly reaffirmed its previous financial...
